    "en": {
      "title": "Flag Stealer Arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A Colombo magistrate has ordered the man who stole the official flag of the President to be remanded until August 05.",
        "After the presidential palace was seized by the protesters on the 9th, a protester was lying on the bed with the presidential flag spread as a blanket.",
        "The person was arrested by the police based on a video posted on social media.",
        "Police said he was arrested for illegally entering the presidential palace and insulting the presidential flag."
      ],
